content: <?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>  <!-- JNLP File for SKTEditor Application -->  <jnlp       spec="1.0"       codebase="http://sscweb.gsfc.nasa.gov/skteditor"      href="skteditor.jnlp">       <information>         <title>ISTP CDF Skeleton Editor</title>         <vendor>NASA/Goddard Space Flight Center</vendor>         <homepage href="index.html"/>         <description>ISTP CDF Skeleton Editor</description>         <description kind="short">SKTEditor</description>         <icon href="nasaball.gif"/>         <offline-allowed/>         <shortcut online="false">            <desktop />            <menu submenu="NASA-GSFC-SPDF" />        </shortcut>      </information>       <security>           <all-permissions/>       </security>       <resources>         <jar href="spdfjavaClasses.jar" main="true" />         <jar href="skteditor-help.jar" />         <extension name="cdf" href="cdf/cdf-latest.jnlp" />        <extension name="CdfValidation" href="CdfValidation/CdfValidation.jnlp" />        <extension name="JavaHelp" href="JavaHelp/JavaHelp.jnlp" />        <property name="cdf.checksum"                  value="MD5" />        <!-- for JRE > 1.6.0_10        <property name="jnlp.packEnabled"                  value="true" />        <property name="swing.defaultlaf"                  value="com.sun.java.swing.plaf.nimbus.NimbusLookAndFeel" />        end JRE > 1.6.0_10 -->        <j2se version="1.6+" /> <!-- Causes the menu to not appear at all with Java 1.5.0_19 and 1.6.0_13      (Apple bug #6975997) until the user selects a different Java window      and then returns to this application's window -->        <property name="apple.laf.useScreenMenuBar"                  value="true" />         <property name="apple.awt.showGrowBox"                  value="true" />        <property name="apple.awt.brushMetalLook"                 value="true" />        <property name="apple.awt.antialiasing"                  value="true" />        <property name="com.apple.mrj.application.apple.menu.about.name"                 value="SKTEditor" />        <property name="com.apple.mrj.application.growbox.inturdes"                  value="true" />      </resources>      <application-desc main-class="gsfc.spdf.edit.guis.SKTEditor"/>  </jnlp>
